These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican
2 different games are played: chess, poker
2 different pets are kept: cat, fish
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, september
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, pink
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, taxi
1. the mexican is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality         | mexican  | brazilian       |
| Game           | poker   | chess    |
| Pet   | fish     | cat   |
| Birthday   | september      | october     |
| Color         | pink | yellow      |
| Transport     | taxi       | bus           |

