2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who likes amber is in an even position##4
6. the blend-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
